        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Broadband Consumer Transparency Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Federal Communications Commission to promulgate regulations that promote and incentivize the widespread adoption of specified broadband consumer labels to disclose to consumers information regarding broadband internet access service plans. </p>]]>
        </text>
